Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Mismis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I bought you the soda pop\Nyou like so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Ginger ale!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Nene and Jhin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't this a treat? Not canned,\Nbut bottled drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mismis, where are you at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Risya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not whining about the many\Nmaterials to memorize, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Issy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind coming over?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To your place, Risya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. To Imperial Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\bord0.25\an8\pos(620,148)\c&H151618&}Our Last Crusade or the Rise of a New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\b0\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\pos(150,604)\clip(50,560,96,682)\t(0,400,\clip(50,560,244,682))}Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, Successor of the Black Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord1\b0\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\pos(302,626)\clip(286,536,332,678)\t(0,800,\clip(286,536,788,658))}Successor of the Black Steel\Nand the Ice Calamity Witch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We reviewed your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought against the Ice Calamity Witch\Nand held her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are a gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I failed to protect the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission we gave you was\Nto stop the Ice Calamity Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to protect the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empire has the fighting power\Nto go against the Ice Calamity Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That knowledge alone is a\Nremarkable military achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So much so that the reinstation\Nas a Saint Disciple is up in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We also understand your determination\Ntowards attaining peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Saint Disciple, you could gain\Nan audience with His Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you are a well-known\Ncriminal within the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we are offering you a new condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Apprehend the Ice Calamity Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We are counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you like this artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So how old are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to skip tomorrow's training session?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to do in Neutral city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But you just went to the art exhibition\Nwith Risya's ticket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going there to see something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somebody I'd like to speak to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you want to skip the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Could you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't say no if you\Nfeel that strongly about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Under one condition...\NI'm going with you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you looked strained right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I can't let a team member\Nin that condition go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in good conscious, as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Then please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to repay you for showing me\Nthe way to the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the dossier on that Imperial swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A Saint Disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Disciple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He was apparently the youngest\Nin history to be promoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt he's one of the most talented\Nswordsmen the Empire has ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how could I have not known?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After his promotion,\Nhe hasn't set foot on a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His promotion was retracted\Nand then he was imprisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he freed an astral mage\Nimprisoned by the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Nelka forest, Iska was after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, find out who this astral mage\Nwas that he freed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already on it. I'll need few more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you have a strong interest\Nin this enemy soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empire is our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A nation full of people who hate\Nand persecute us, calling us witches...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The way we were treated by the Empire was\Nnothing short of a cruel witch hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless astral mages fell victim to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To defeat and overthrow the Empire\Nis us astral mages' dearest wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial artists are no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about the numerous paintings\Nof the "witch hunt" and "witch trials."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They, too, are pawns of the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is inexcusable to collect things like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have taken enough of your time\Nso late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, are you around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Her Majesty say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Be prepared to take me\Nto Neutral city first thing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?! But if we bump\Ninto that soldier, Iska, again--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm counting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to figure out his true intent for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Iska. Care to tell me who it is\Nyou've arranged this meeting with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling she'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never believed in fate\Nor destiny until now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something that I want to make sure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how rare! It's an albatross!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many live in the Empire territory anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I think a few villages\Nin the outskirts tame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, please keep going until the entrance,\Nand then stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We really do have a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, what kind of a star\Nwe were born under?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My boss, Captain Mismis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's why you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Iska... Who's the pretty girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, captain from the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aliceliese Lou Nebulis IX.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Alice? But, wait, "Nebulis"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the people of the Empire may\Nknow me better as the Ice Calamity Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why we hate each other\Nwhen there are peaceful cities like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A year ago, an Imperial soldier\Nwas arrested for treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A peculiar Saint Disciple who freed\Nan astral mage taken captive by the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve or 13 years old, with weak astral power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Empire wishes to apprehend\Nall astral mages regardless of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your actions are contradicting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You came after me in\Nthe Nelka forest to capture me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But a year ago, you freed someone because\Nyou pitied her? That's not convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost your voice? What's wrong, Imperial soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't contradicting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal hasn't changed.\NNot now, and not a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A peace negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to end the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Empire won't act\Nbased on anything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither will the Nebulis Sovereignty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So my plan was to take a direct\Ndescendant of Nebulis hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A powerful astral mage, or purebred,\Nas the Empire calls them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured if royalty was in danger,\Nit would faze the Nebulis Sovereignty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Their people will also be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It would force them to respond\Nto the peace negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But that won't work. Nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you take me hostage,\NMother will not react.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So there won't be a negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace is just a pipe dream. You've never\Nbeen to the Sovereignty, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how many people\Nin our nation loath the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also never knew the Empire\Nhad people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the barbaric and\Ncoercive Imperial soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew there was someone\Nwho wants to fight for the end of this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides... I think I got\Nto know you pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You should serve under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait, Lady Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not what we discussed\Nat yesterday's meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It just came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither Lady Elletear or Lady Sisbell\Nwill allow that, let alone Her Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cross that bridge when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll guarantee your social status.\NYou will defect from the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Iska...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but my astral power\Nis frightened as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Mismis, fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Astral sword... Treacherous...\Nblade... of the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The... Founder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Iska? Did she just say the Founder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's exactly what you're thinking,\NCaptain Mismis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Witch Nebulis is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:14:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred years ago, when she turned\Nthe Empire into a sea of flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't fair! It's just me\Nand Iska on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empire... Those who corrode\Nthis planet and its astral power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They should all perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mow them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Every astral power\Nin the Sovereignty is resonating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Founder's bond...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With her power, the Empire's defeat\Nis within arm's reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the Founder your ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Nebulis call her the Founder\Nbecause she created our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To call her an ally would be sheer arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, why would the Founder go\Nafter Alice, her own descendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the astral power's auto defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I don't know what it's reacting to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lady Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How frustrating...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Frustrating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to settle this\Njust between the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I met you in the Neutral city,\NI've had this {\i1}feeling{\i0} inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a princess, that's not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came here today to quash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really fired up about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted just the two of us to settle this,\Nwithout anyone's meddling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And of all people, the stupid Founder\Nwaltzes in between us and ruins it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we won't get anywhere\Nif we just stand here. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop this, Founder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,An astral mage dares to get in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are joining forces with the Empire...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then vanish off the face of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin! Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, please open your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool Rin's body with ice.\NThat's what your astral power is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Mismis, please take her to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Preferably to an astral injury specialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And also order the residents\Nto evacuate the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This field is about to become\Na very dangerous area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those the swords that have awakened me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are Crossweil's swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Crossweil?! How do you know Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're his...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter. You cannot possibly stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An astral mage taking sides with the Empire...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No amount of screaming\Nwill save you from your sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're also an astral mage, but you've hurt\Nan ally without so much as a blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the hero of the Sovereignty anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hero? You cannot save the world\Nwith such a pretty word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I will become a witch\Nand destroy the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nebulis, you may have been the hope\Nthat lead all astral mages 100 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing your actions made me understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, in this age...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You are no longer needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Imperial soldier. Astral mage. You two--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your actions are hollow and meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The future I strive for is not with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither is the world I strive for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So go back to sleep for another hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empire's lap dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how many astral mages\Nwere oppressed by the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She uses both ice and earth astral powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Ice Calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the planet's wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of your hand! You'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think we're feeling the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, you're upset because Rin was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And a peace negotiation is out\Nthe window with her rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is neither the Empire nor the Sovereignty.\NWe're in Neutral city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We share the same goal.\NThat's all that matters. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really trust someone from the Empire...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice Calamity: Flooding Snow Lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot up, Star of Ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So aves cal pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Crawl the earth like the pathetic dog you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Insolence. You have no idea\Nthe quarrel I have with the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of your vendetta\Nthat this ridiculous war won't end!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloom forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to sleep, Nebulis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time you awake, the world\Nwill be a slightly better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, about what you said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.37,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't flip to the Nebulis' side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you and I are enemies after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd like to propose one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A temporary truce... I'm spent for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No objections here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for today, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we're back to being enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.12,0:23:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.